Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Sentinel ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Sentinel Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.202	DESC:Sentinels are proficient with all simple and martial weapons, with all types of armor (heavy, medium, and light), and with shields (except tower shields).	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=WeaponProfMartial|TYPE=ArmorProfHeavy|TYPE=ShieldProf
